answersResultList.title: You can predict random events.
answersResultList.resultContent: Some people read the NASDAQ index, calculate the odds, or consult their horoscopes. You just know. Whether it's a squirrel missing a branch, the first name of the next lottery winner, or your favorite politician saying something dumb, you see it coming. Of course, the operative word is 'random,' so you can't exactly take this to the bank...

answersResultList.title: You can read people's moods.
answersResultList.resultContent: Maybe it's the color of their aura or changes in their breathing. Maybe it's how they enter a room or what's in their eyes when they smile. Whatever tips you off, you know when to be supportive, make a joke, or warn bystanders to clear the area. If animals are drawn to you, this is probably why.
